{
  "stem": "13315.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they advised, take one of the freighters that doesn't stop anywhere until it gets you in the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there was a Norwegian freighter, but went for a Manila shipping company-- copper boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They transported copper to the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, I was one of seven passengers on that boat-- so that got me over to the States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Where did you arrive at?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I should have arrived in San Francisco, but there was a big strike on, so I got off the boat in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought, why should I wait until we sooner or later land in San Francisco?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got off the boat in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wrote to him in Vienna, and then I got-- from the [NON-ENGLISH] in Chicago, I got a cable.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I should transfer $150 through them so that Father and his wife could get the ticket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have any $150.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But through-- let's say luck, in a way-- there was a very wealthy Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people who gave me the affidavit knew him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was willing to sell my camera-- my photo-- my stamp collection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Find a buyer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the man-- I talked to him-- said, why do you want to sell it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I need the money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I showed him the wire from the [NON-ENGLISH] in Italy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to send the money, or they won't be able to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, forget the stamps, made out a check-- $150.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then, later on, as soon as-- I was then married, already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As soon as Martha and I had the money, we saw him and gave it back to him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a multimillionaire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What's his name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't want to mention the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a multimillionaire, very fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
